# --- GoSPA Global Docker Ignore ---

# Git & Tooling
.git/
.github/
.vscode/
.idea/
.golangci.yml
CHANGELOG.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
LICENSE
plans/

# Large Binaries & Assets
*.psd
*.jpeg
*.png
*.ico
*.svg
*.webp
!website/static/**

# Build Artifacts
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/generated/
**/tmp_build/

# Specific Root Binaries (Must use '/' prefix to avoid ignoring 'cmd/gospa')
/gospa
/website/website
/website/website.bin

# Go Cache & Logs
lint.log
lint.txt
go.work.bak
*.test
*_test.go

# Project Specific (Optional)
# Don't ignore things needed for the website build
examples/
scripts/
tests/
# docs/ - Documentation website often needs this!
